{"html":"<div class=\"hypothesis-box\"><div class=\"hypothesis-box-header\">仮説 #1</div><div class=\"hypothesis-meta-text\">基づくキーワード: エネルギー政策</div><div class=\"hypothesis-box-body\"><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"hypothesis-text\" placeholder=\"ここに仮説を入力\" data-last-logged-value=\"\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">aaaa</textarea></div><div class=\"scamper-tags\"><div class=\"scamper-tag-container\"><span class=\"scamper-tag\" data-key=\"Combine\">結合 (Combine)</span><span class=\"scamper-question-view\">太陽光発電と水力発電の利点を結びつけると、どのような新しい発電システムが生まれる可能性がありますか？</span><div class=\"hypothesis-action-bar\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button add-node-button\">ノード追加</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-action-button scamper-button\">仮説を発散</button></div><textarea class=\"scamper-edit-box\" placeholder=\"発散させた仮説を記入してください\" data-last-logged-value=\"aaaa\" data-logging-bound=\"true\" data-has-action-bar=\"true\">aaaa</textarea></div></div><div class=\"hypothesis-controls\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hypothesis-delete-btn\">削除</button></div></div>"}